# Fractions
snippet / "Fraction" i
\\frac{${VISUAL}}{$1}$0
endsnippet

snippet // "Fraction" i
\\frac{$1}{$2}$0
endsnippet

snippet '((\d+)|(\d*)(\\)?([A-Za-z]+)((\^|_)(\{\d+\}|\d))*)/' "Fraction" wr
\\frac{`!p snip.rv = match.group(1)`}{$1}$0
endsnippet

